title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Aircraft & Avionics Update - New beta build
description:
In this video we will go through the changes in the latest beta build of Aircraft & Avionics Update (AAU) 1 which has been released yesterday. The new build contains several fixes for issues reported by beta testers as well as a stability fix for the Xbox based on the content of the release notes.
